Prerequisites
Hypervisor: VMware, Hyper-V, or VirtualBox

Windows Server ISO (2016/2019/2022)

Windows 10/11 Pro/Enterprise ISO

Minimum 8GB RAM (16GB recommended)

100GB+ free storage

Lab Architecture
Domain Controller (Windows Server)
├── AD DS + DNS + DHCP
├── Group Policy Management
├── File Server Role
└── FSRM

Client Machines (Windows 10/11)
├── Domain-joined
└── GPO testing
